    {
      "type": "FUNCTION",
      "name": "b2d.shape.set_shape",
      "brief": "Set a shape's geometry.",
      "description": "This updates the shape geometry using the same table format as\n<code>b2d.body.create_shape</code> and <code>b2d.shape.get_shape</code>. The body mass is not\nupdated unless <code>update_mass</code> is true.",
      "returnvalues": [],
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "shape_id",
          "doc": "shape handle from a shape info table, or pass <code>body, shape_index</code>",
          "types": ["b2Shape"],
          "is_optional": "False"
        },
        {
          "name": "definition",
          "doc": "shape table with numeric <code>type</code> from <code>b2d.shape.SHAPE_TYPE_*</code>",
          "types": ["table"],
          "is_optional": "False"
        },
        {
          "name": "update_mass",
          "doc": "true to reset body mass from shapes",
          "types": ["boolean"],
          "is_optional": "False"
        }
      ],
      "examples": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">local</span> <span class=\"n\">body</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get_body</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;#collisionobject&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Move a circle shape relative to the body origin.</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">local</span> <span class=\"n\">circle</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">get_shape</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">body</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">circle</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">center</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">vmath</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vector3</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">24</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set_shape</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">body</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">circle</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Replace a segment shape&#39;s local endpoints.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set_shape</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">body</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"nb\">type</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SHAPE_TYPE_SEGMENT</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">v1</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">vmath</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vector3</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">v2</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">vmath</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vector3</span><span class=\"p\">(</span> <span class=\"mi\">32</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"p\">})</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- Update a box shape using the polygon box convenience format.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set_shape</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">body</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"nb\">type</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">b2d</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SHAPE_TYPE_BOX</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">hx</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">16</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">hy</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">center</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">vmath</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vector3</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">20</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">angle</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">math.rad</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">30</span><span class=\"p\">),</span>\n<span class=\"p\">},</span> <span class=\"kc\">true</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
      "replaces": "",
      "error": "",
      "tparams": [],
      "members": [],
      "notes": [],
      "language": ""
